original_sql: SELECT * FROM title t,cast_info ci,movie_info_idx mi_idx WHERE t.id=ci.movie_id AND t.id=mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.person_id>681261 AND ci.role_id>1 AND mi_idx.info_type_id=99;
rewritten_sql: SELECT * FROM title AS title59 INNER JOIN (SELECT * FROM cast_info WHERE person_id > 681261 AND role_id > 1) AS t213 ON title59.id = t213.movie_id INNER JOIN (SELECT * FROM movie_info_idx WHERE info_type_id = 99) AS t214 ON title59.id = t214.movie_id

original_sql: SELECT * FROM title t,movie_companies mc WHERE t.id=mc.movie_id AND t.kind_id=7 AND mc.company_id>506;
rewritten_sql: SELECT * FROM (SELECT * FROM title WHERE kind_id = 7) AS t INNER JOIN (SELECT * FROM movie_companies WHERE company_id > 506) AS t0 ON t.id = t0.movie_id;
